OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely dry across the region
OL,6,Ftoday with some early mist patches.
OL,7,FSunny spells at first, but clouding
OL,8,Fover a little during the afternoon,
OL,9,Fwith some spells of hazy sunshine.
OL,10,FLess windy than Saturday.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloud breaking up a little
OL,13,Fduring the evening to bring some ate
OL,14,Fsunshine to end the day. Turning
OL,15,Fchilly overnight under the clear
OL,16,Fspells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
