OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA few early showers possible
OL,6,Fin the south, but a drier and brighter
OL,7,Fstart elsewhere. Clouding over through
OL,8,Fthe morning with showery outbreaks of
OL,9,Frain possible through the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FSpells
OL,12,Fof rain possible at times over the
OL,13,Fnext few days, but some drier,
OL,14,Fbrighter and warmers intervals in
OL,15,Fbetween. Breezy at times and
OL,16,Ftemperatures around the seasonal
OL,17,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
